#Tools

###Sublime Text 2

If [Sublime Text 2](http://www.sublimetext.com/2) is your editor of choice, download the app and install [Package Control](http://wbond.net/sublime_packages/package_control/installation).

*If you are on the Foxtel network, manually install package control and set the package control user settings to the following config to bypass proxies:*

```
{
  "http_proxy": "192.168.100.218:3128",
  "https_proxy": "192.168.100.218:3128",
  "repository_channels":
  [
    "http://sublime.wbond.net/repositories.json"
  ],
  "submit_url": "http://sublime.wbond.net/submit"
}
```

Now install any packages required.